{
  "name": "@lotaber_wang/openclaw-dc-plugin",
  "version": "0.1.11",
  "type": "module",
  "description": "TapTap DC 的 OpenClaw 插件，内置原始数据工具与运营简报 skill；如需重启 Gateway，应先提示用户。",
  "main": "index.js",
  "openclaw": {
    "extensions": [
      "./index.js"
    ],
    "install": {
      "npmSpec": "@lotaber_wang/openclaw-dc-plugin",
      "postInstallMessage": "TapTap DC 插件已安装完成。OpenClaw 接下来如需重启 Gateway，应先提示用户；重启完成后即可使用 taptap_dc_* 工具。",
      "restartRequired": true,
      "restartCommand": "openclaw gateway restart",
      "instructions": [
        "如果安装流程判断需要重启 Gateway，先通知用户，再执行重启。",
        "推荐提示文案：TapTap DC 插件已安装完成。OpenClaw 接下来如需重启 Gateway，应先提示用户；重启完成后即可使用 taptap_dc_* 工具。",
        "执行顺序：先提示用户 -> 再执行 gateway restart -> 重启完成后再开始使用 taptap_dc_* 工具。"
      ]
    }
  },
  "exports": {
    ".": "./index.js",
    "./package.json": "./package.json"
  },
  "publishConfig": {
    "access": "public"
  },
  "bundleDependencies": [
    "@mikoto_zero/minigame-open-mcp"
  ],
  "files": [
    "index.js",
    "lib/",
    "openclaw.plugin.json",
    "skills/",
    "README.md"
  ],
  "keywords": [
    "openclaw",
    "openclaw-plugin",
    "taptap",
    "dc",
    "skill"
  ],
  "engines": {
    "node": ">=18.14.1"
  },
  "license": "MIT",
  "peerDependencies": {
    "openclaw": ">=2026.1.29"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@mikoto_zero/minigame-open-mcp": "^1.19.0"
  },
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "git+https://github.com/taptap/taptap_minigame_open_mcp.git",
    "directory": "packages/openclaw-dc-plugin"
  },
  "homepage": "https://github.com/taptap/taptap_minigame_open_mcp/tree/main/packages/openclaw-dc-plugin",
  "bugs": {
    "url": "https://github.com/taptap/taptap_minigame_open_mcp/issues"
  }
}
